# No Dividers in Comments

Do not use `---`, `===`, `───`, or any other horizontal rule/divider syntax in code comments. No ASCII dividers, no Unicode box-drawing dividers.

Section headers in comments are just words:

```rust
// BAD:
// ---
// === Section ===
// ── Section ──────────────────────────────────────────────

// GOOD:
// Section
```
